rows.label: qev086901_MSG0001
rows.name: You seem to be working hard, Rock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0002
rows.name: Hi, Celica! Hi, everyone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0003
rows.name:
We were in the area, so we thought we
might drop by to say hi and see you in action.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0004
rows.name: Thanks! I really love my job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0005
rows.name:
I don't have to feel scared,
and everyone seems to appreciate what I do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0006
rows.name: That sound great![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0007
rows.name:
Tatsu still looking for workplace where
unique talents will be appreciated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0008
rows.name: Can you all wait a few minutes? It's almost my break.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0009
rows.name: Of course! We'll just hang out here and watch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0010
rows.name: Gosh, it feels funny having an audience.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0011
rows.name: Hey, Rock! Can I get a hand over here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0012
rows.name: On my way![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0013
rows.name: Seems like he's having fun.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0014
rows.name:
We have the director general to thank
for getting him this position.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0015
rows.name: Yeah, I guess we do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0016
rows.name: Look out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0017
rows.name: Rock, get back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0018
rows.name: Aaah![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0019
rows.name: Hey, are you all right?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086901_MSG0020
rows.name: Oh, no![ST:wait ]
